        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 38. Old tree of Agathis dammara (Chambert, 1803) in the forest of Mt. Salak-Halimun National Park (Java) with resin secretion; A. Basal trunk with several outpourings; B. Close-up of an outpouring caused by mechanical damage (photo: W. Mey)." , "Figure 33. Agathiphagama perdita gen. nov., sp. nov., female holotype, photographed submerged in glycerine." , "Figure 32. Agathiphagama perdita gen. nov., sp. nov., female holotype." , "Figures 12 - 17. Agathiphagama perdita gen. nov., sp. nov., female holotype; 12. Head, lateral view; 13. Foreleg; 14. Middle and hind leg; 15. Wing venation; 16. Forewing scales; 17. Postabdomen and oviscapt. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/518735" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/518730" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/518729" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/518726" .

